name: Ui Kit first project
description:
A free UI Kit for desktop


The composition includes :

-components

-styles

-icons

-grids.


The components include: accordion menu, buttons, switches, radio buttons, checkboxes, tables, modal windows, tags, notification windows, inputs, vertical and horizontal menus, switches, text field, drop-down lists.


Styles contain icons: Feather Icons, Phosphor Icons.
